{"tid":2162795,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"加國集會領唱《願榮光》  鄭敬基：一齊幫香港","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T16:08:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"40d19060b3561d553f70a3cb0d4f32216abd60d6","tid":2162795,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200818/WNB7UNLBBVG4DILW6M2JM2JGEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200818%2FWNB7UNLBBVG4DILW6M2JM2JGEU%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkFxw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=60551e8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200818%2FWNB7UNLBBVG4DILW6M2JM2JGEU%2F&h=1ccc55c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200818/WNB7UNLBBVG4DILW6M2JM2JGEU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n加國集會領唱《願榮光》 <br />\n鄭敬基：一齊幫香港<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英上周一被拘捕，警方更大規模佔領搜查《蘋果》大樓，引起各界不滿。前日加拿大各省市有多批人士舉辦撐港集會聲援，身在多倫多的鄭敬基於胸前戴上撐《蘋果》襟章，現身當地集會，手持蘋果帶領數百人一起合唱《願榮光歸香港》，他說：「希望有更多喺加拿大嘅香港人出嚟，一齊幫香港。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【外地發聲】手足齊打國際線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sKpwbKKyFrcoX9IbaG0P0Fa3tIU=/640x327/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JG6YP3BB2FHTFKMRT5O435FF4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsKpwbKKyFrcoX9IbaG0P0Fa3tIU%3D%2F640x327%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJG6YP3BB2FHTFKMRT5O435FF4E.jpg&h=ead84787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭敬基與太太Angie前日在加拿大多倫多出席撐港集會，他除了領唱《願榮光歸香港》外，更手持《蘋果日報》撐壹傳媒。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n香港警方上周一以國安法之名拘捕壹傳媒。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jDCgABmtBJQZqOPXwrkkHfb4w3g=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ALWKB7B3J5GL7BGC7E6RYL5WT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjDCgABmtBJQZqOPXwrkkHfb4w3g%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FALWKB7B3J5GL7BGC7E6RYL5WT4.jpg&h=ea1080cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭敬基表示即使因為演唱《願榮光》而沒有其他機會唱歌，他也不會介意。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Jd2oLPn0W-V0z3OuUCaTKBhN9yw=/640x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YY6UARNGX5FQBPUI7JP34RS5G4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJd2oLPn0W-V0z3OuUCaTKBhN9yw%3D%2F640x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYY6UARNGX5FQBPUI7JP34RS5G4.jpg&h=00a77cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■移居加國的鄭敬基積極打國際戰線，早前與太太在當地見國會議員，為香港發聲。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手持蘋果撐《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n加拿大時間前日，身穿黑衣戴上黃色口罩、胸前戴上撐《蘋果》襟章的鄭敬基，現身多倫多一個支持港人抗爭集會，他拿起咪以英語發言：「哪怕失去我所有的歌曲，我寧願只懂得這一首歌，大家一起唱吧！《願榮光歸香港》！光復香港！」隨後在場不同種族膚色的數百名聲援人士一起大合唱，不少人更高舉「五一」手勢，又揮舞旗幟及標語。<br />\n<br />\n唱畢《願榮光歸香港》後，鄭敬基手持一個新鮮蘋果，帶領在場人士大叫「光復香港！時代革命！營救手足！」大量網民看畢片段後，都留言多謝鄭敬基及「海外手足」，更稱「全世界唯一一首歌，乜人唱都一樣有咁好聽！」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》昨日聯絡鄭敬基，他說：「。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NH_7XAzxXBTx1FtksomjCbZMo2U=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OQG6KWXUPRHANCOKVNIWTRQ27Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNH_7XAzxXBTx1FtksomjCbZMo2U%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOQG6KWXUPRHANCOKVNIWTRQ27Q.jpg&h=86531f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫哥華 ■加拿大各省市前日舉行「制裁中共營救手足大集會」，除聲援香港手足外，也有人拿着蘋果以示支持黎智英及《蘋果》。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m16aa_OMsWyoVbfL2H0Re1mnLJA=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TYWZ7PZH4ZGELL4JKNDDGGCIKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm16aa_OMsWyoVbfL2H0Re1mnLJA%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTYWZ7PZH4ZGELL4JKNDDGGCIKI.jpg&h=cbf04c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬錦市 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QijIDVu6r1Cqqy04h7AFOajcjWA=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DJSWCIQ52VG4BELNNVJSAH5XQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQijIDVu6r1Cqqy04h7AFOajcjWA%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDJSWCIQ52VG4BELNNVJSAH5XQ4.jpg&h=549c36d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛民頓 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r3oiFz0Eg8_f9QEPX8RYtwakvf4=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RLAFO6ZQSZD77ELVHAMPBPAXSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fr3oiFz0Eg8_f9QEPX8RYtwakvf4%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRLAFO6ZQSZD77ELVHAMPBPAXSU.jpg&h=b4def701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卡加利 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驚訝有內地人參加<br />\n<br />\n鄭敬基又指：「加埋都有成700人，最感動係有西藏代表、台灣代表、仲有越南、維吾爾，最驚訝有啲係內地嚟，佢哋叫自己做『中國民主黨』，大部份都識唱《榮光》，好多加拿大嘅香港人到晒，又拎住個蘋果一齊唱。」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n敢言的鄭敬基去年開始積極關注社會運動，並跟太太Angie參加遊行，。。。。。。。。。。，又去見加拿大國會議員Erin Otoole，向他表示香港極需要得到國際支援。"},{"pid":"a6bf0080727102db12975b17cbee0409b9104ba8","tid":2162795,"uid":328267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:59:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"83a316ebb91a907b39a1956e92fbec724d8edb74","tid":2162795,"uid":15567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:00:31.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/n